lead_paragraph: Real Madrid have no intention of making a quick profit on striker Alvaro Morata after the Champions League winners opted to take him back to the Bernabeu from Juventus last month, the Spanish side's manager Zinedine Zidane has said.

headline.print_headline: Zidane Insists Morata Is Staying at Real Madrid
headline.main: Zidane Insists Morata Is Staying at Real Madrid
